From 3b1434ddf88ae29e0e13686bb5671cb4242f05f9 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sushant Butta <sbutta@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Tue, 1 Jul 2025 01:00:40 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 01/10] UPSTREAM: DP: wifi: ath12k: Rx Filter setp and cleanup

With the Filter framework, a 2D array of Rx TLV filter object
is allocated to hold filters for multiple features
(such as stats mode and monitor mode).
This design provides the flexibility to configure filters
based on the specific feature and its requirements.
The allocation and deallocation of the 2D filter array object
is performed dynamically.

Patch-dependency:
	0404-0006-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Refactor-monitor-Rx-hal-TLV-.patch

Signed-off-by: Sushant Butta <sbutta@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/Makefile      |  3 +-
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/dp_mon.h      | 15 ++++
 .../net/wireless/ath/ath12k/dp_mon_filter.c   | 76 +++++++++++++++++++
 .../net/wireless/ath/ath12k/dp_mon_filter.h   | 35 +++++++++
 .../net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/dp_mon1.c   |  3 +
 .../net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/dp_mon2.c   |  3 +
